name: SOMETIMES I FEEL I LIVE IN A GODARD FILM
description: Spontaneity in art. 2K seamless videoloop. You and your clone, walk the line. Experimenting new lightning techniques with plastic and paper, shot on an IPhone 8 in the street. I don´t know the graffiti artist name, but it was shot in Alejandro Dumas street in Guadalajara, México, 2020.
